Coder's tool whitelist is `["read", "bash", "edit", "write"]`. The `lint` and `typecheck` tools registered by lint-guard are NOT active. Coder can't manually invoke lint. Must rely entirely on auto-lint + vague "Verify your changes compile/work" instruction.

### Issue 5: Coder system prompt is vague (Minor)
`- Verify your changes compile/work` doesn't specifically instruct the coder to wait for lint results, fix lint errors, or use any particular verification approach.

